<title>AUSTRALIA: Century recommends Downer's revised offer.</title>
<headline>Century recommends Downer's revised offer.</headline>
<dateline>SYDNEY 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Century Drilling Ltd said on Tuesday it recommended acceptance of the revised A$1.60 per share takeover offer from Downer Group Australia Pty Ltd, a unit of Paul Y-Construction Holdings Ltd.</p>
